1. Ja se baziram na znanju koje sam stekao na fakultetu. (*bazi*ram) (I base myself on the knowledge I gained in college.)
2. Ovaj posao ima čvrste *baze* u industriji. (*baze*) (This job has solid foundations in the industry.)
3. Ona ima jako dobru *bazu* znanja iz matematike. (*bazu*) (She has a very good knowledge base in mathematics.)
4. Potrebno je da imamo čvrstu *bazu* podataka za ovaj projekt. (*bazu*) (We need a solid database for this project.)
5. *Bazira* se na pretpostavkama koje nisu dokazane. (*Bazira*) (It is based on assumptions that are not proven.)
6. Naš plan je da se *bazira* na novim tehnologijama. (*bazira*) (Our plan is to be based on new technologies.)
7. On je *baziran* u Beogradu, ali putuje često. (*baziran*) (He is based in Belgrade, but he travels frequently.)
8. Njegova tvrtka je *bazirana* na proizvodnji sportske opreme. (*bazirana*) (His company is based on sports equipment manufacturing.)
9. *Bazeći se* na prethodnom iskustvu, znam kako da se nosim s ovim izazovom. (*Bazeći se*) (Based on previous experience, I know how to handle this challenge.)
10. Mi smo odlučili da se *baziramo* na digitalnom marketingu. (*baziramo*) (We have decided to base ourselves on digital marketing.)